platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Simply Guitar is all about you: your skills, your pace, and your comfort levels. No experience is neededthe app actually starts by asking if you even own a guitarand after a few quick questions about your skill level and background, youll be on your way to learning with tracks like Queens We Will Rock You, Aretha Franklins Chain of Fools, and Billie Eilishs Bad Guy. To help you grow your skills, Simply Guitar uses live feedback: It will recognize what youre playing and provide real-time tips on your strum patterns and D chords. Start with basics, follow the lessons, and work your way up to power chordsyou'll be playing lead guitar in no time.

Learn to play guitar at your own pace, no experience necessary. Just give the app your skill level and youll be on your way. Grow from the basics with live feedback, which provides real-time tips so youll be playing lead guitar in no time.
